			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Another thing i found handy is instead of using &lt;t&gt; use your group members name. It has alowed me to heal members much more quickly then the other way. For example:
<br />

<br />
/ta Valarm
<br />
/magic Cure
<br />
/pa Valarm
<br />

<br />
The only down side is rembering which macro is which and you have to edit each every time you join a new party. Thus what I do in limit that type of Macro to 4 members of the group usally the tanks or low HP members.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
