			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You can go one step further, and have a macro line for each member of the party. (0 - 5).
<br />

<br />
So 
<br />
CTRL-0 /ma Cure &lt;p0&gt;
<br />
CTRL-1 /ma Cure &lt;p1&gt;
<br />
CTRL-2 /ma Cure &lt;p2&gt;
<br />
CTRL-3 /ma Cure &lt;p3&gt;
<br />
CTRL-4 /ma Cure &lt;p4&gt;
<br />
CTRL-5 /ma Cure &lt;p5&gt;
<br />

<br />
Then you can put whatever you want in 6-9 (I put Dia, Bene and my "&lt;t&gt; going agro on me, Provoke! Provoke!").
<br />

<br />
If you are a healer with these macros, you parties will love you, you will be able to get a heal off at anyone in the group nealy instantly.
<br />

<br />
If you SHOULD heal just anyone in your party aside from the tank is another matter entirely, but any group you get in, you will already have an insta-heal macro for the tank and no hitting tab.
<br />

<br />
-Dystar</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
